          "type": "matrix-radio",
          "location": "belowStimulus",
          "prompt": "**Q1** - Which **rhetorical techniques** may have **contributed** to making this visualization **misleading**, and how significant is each one's contribution?**&nbsp;**",
          "secondaryText": "Consider both tweet text and visualizations.<br>Select 'None' if a technique does not apply, or 'I don’t know' if you are unsure.",
          "answerOptions": [
            "I don't know",
            "None",
            "Minimal",
            "Limited",
            "Moderate",
            "Considerable",
            "Strong",
            "Very Strong"
          ],
          "questionOptions": [
            "Information Access Rhetoric",
            "Provenance Rhetoric",
            "Mapping Rhetoric",
            "Linguistic Based Rhetoric",
            "Procedural Rhetoric"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "intents",
          "type": "matrix-radio",
          "location": "belowStimulus",
          "prompt": "**Q2** - Which **author's intentions** may have **contributed** to making this visualization **misleading**, and how significant is each one's contribution?**&nbsp;**",
          "secondaryText": "Consider both tweet text and visualizations.<br>Select 'None' if an intent does not apply, or 'I don’t know' if you are unsure.",
          "answerOptions": [
            "I don't know",
            "None",
            "Minimal",
            "Limited",
            "Moderate",
            "Considerable",
            "Strong",
            "Very Strong"
          ],
          "questionOptions": [
           "Aesthetic-Driven Misrepresentation",
           "Bias Exploitation",
           "Claim-Supporting Manipulation",
           "Context Distortion",
           "Deliberate Reader Confusion",
           "Lack of Visualization Literacy",
           "Selective Reporting",
           "Space and Format Constraints",
           "Unintentional Context Omission"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "commentsOnIntents",
          "prompt": "**Q3** - Are there **other intents**, not listed above, that may have **contributed** to making this visualization misleading? If so, please describe them.",
          "required": false,
          "location": "belowStimulus",
          "type": "longText",
          "placeholder": "Type your answer here..."
        },
        {
          "id": "intentionality",
          "type": "matrix-radio",
          "location": "belowStimulus",
          "prompt": "**Q4** - Overall, how much do you think the **misleading aspects** of this visualization may have been **intentional**, rather than **accidental** (unintentional)?**&nbsp;**",
          "secondaryText": "For example, if the author created (or the tweer author shared) the visualization to intentionally mislead and/or lie.<br>Select 'I don’t know' if you are unsure.",
          "answerOptions": [
            "I don't know",
            "Highly Unintentional",
            "Mostly Unintentional",
            "Slightly Unintentional",
            "Neutral / Unsure",
            "Slightly Intentional",
            "Mostly Intentional",
            "Highly Intentional"
          ],
          "questionOptions": [
            "Intentionally to mislead"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "commentsOnVisualization",
          "prompt": "**Q5** - Any comments you would like to share about this **visualization**?",
          "required": false,
          "location": "belowStimulus",
          "type": "longText",
          "placeholder": "Type your answer here..."
        },
        {
          "id": "commentsOnChoices",
